### Create Patient-Doctor Mapping
POST http://localhost:3000/api/mappings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

{
  "patient_id": 1,
  "doctor_id": 1,
  "notes": "Regular cardiology consultation for hypertension management"
}

### Get All Mappings
GET http://localhost:3000/api/mappings
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Get Doctors for Specific Patient
GET http://localhost:3000/api/mappings/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Delete Patient-Doctor Mapping
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/mappings/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Delete Patient
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/patients/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Delete Doctor
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/doctors/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN